    "name": "美人驾到：忘忧岛",
    "steam_appid": 3111830,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111830/extras/a76c69b7a55ae4902f06bdc1bc4934c8.avif?t=1771101423\" width=620 height=250 /></span><strong>【美人驾到：忘忧岛】是一款模拟经营类的休闲爱情游戏！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款关于爱情的模拟游戏，通过游戏中的日常管理，如打猎、出海获取各种烹饪、制作材料，用来制作各种精美的衣服、食物、珠宝等。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111830/extras/8645b802f4cd68cb8dfc8301cef80e51.poster.avif?t=1771101423\" width=620 height=370 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111830/extras/8645b802f4cd68cb8dfc8301cef80e51.webm?t=1771101423\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111830/extras/8645b802f4cd68cb8dfc8301cef80e51.mp4?t=1771101423\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111830/extras/f0f62cb85a0b343cab9c67d1eea91ce8.avif?t=1771101423\" width=620 height=250 /></span>一个单身了20年的宅男最伟大的梦想是什么？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >请做出以下选择：①征服世界   ②变成大富豪   ③统御美少女</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >开玩笑！上一世啥都没有，没钱没势，连个妞都没泡过，这都穿越了，还让我做选择题？瞧不起谁呢！小孩儿才做选择题，老子统统都要！！！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111830/extras/09825811e608c1ffb55204a2bbd1b26d.poster.avif?t=1771101423\" width=620 height=370 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111830/extras/09825811e608c1ffb55204a2bbd1b26d.webm?t=1771101423\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111830/extras/09825811e608c1ffb55204a2bbd1b26d.mp4?t=1771101423\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111830/extras/2bca2bff9890d6ca4eb611734319a54c.avif?t=1771101423\" width=620 height=250 /></span>丰富的剧情也是这款游戏的一大特色，每一个来到这里的美女都会成为你的情人，和她们聊天、玩耍、一起享受美食，给她们最漂亮的衣服、首饰，并通过这些获得她们的青睐和喜爱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111830/extras/58bd1e9b8fc7dd74921b6915a3e9f7b6.poster.avif?t=1771101423\" width=620 height=372 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111830/extras/58bd1e9b8fc7dd74921b6915a3e9f7b6.webm?t=1771101423\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111830/extras/58bd1e9b8fc7dd74921b6915a3e9f7b6.mp4?t=1771101423\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
